<p class="">Did we not play some part?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-880b5151-93e1-4d5e-ae93-253c5460897d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
