    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">And Europe; but the right hon. Gentleman will not pretend that, by comparison with this large-scale effort, we ourselves could have done what the United States has done.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-d78cc3ef-0f0f-45e8-97f9-475fb8c8995d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-05-01/debates/c220fda6-44ae-48a6-aaf1-a4dfcccad06f/DefenceProgramme(RawMaterialsAndProduction)#contribution-d78cc3ef-0f0f-45e8-97f9-475fb8c8995d">
