                Mr. Jones
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-096036a1-9661-4a06-83e2-17c9c5f694ed" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-05-01/debates/c220fda6-44ae-48a6-aaf1-a4dfcccad06f/DefenceProgramme(RawMaterialsAndProduction)#contribution-096036a1-9661-4a06-83e2-17c9c5f694ed">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The evidence which the hon. Gentleman now adduces is this: His friends who could have bought the ore did not, but held off, waiting for the Government to give them a higher price.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
