    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The hon. Gentleman ought to be fair to the International Nickel Company. If he reads the latest speech of their chairman, he will see that they are in grave doubts about their ore reserve position and that they are trying to find other deposits outside their Sudbury deposits. The discovery of nickel deposits has been very disappointing in recent years. What the hon. Gentleman is really saying is that the mine at Sudbury should be mined faster than it has been. He is a bit off the track if that is his view.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
