                Mr. Fort  (Clitheroe)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-2d9abaf8-36a5-4565-8857-5b0e59557f00" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-05-01/debates/c220fda6-44ae-48a6-aaf1-a4dfcccad06f/DefenceProgramme(RawMaterialsAndProduction)#contribution-2d9abaf8-36a5-4565-8857-5b0e59557f00">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
