                Mr. John Hynd  (Sheffield, Attercliffe)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-389683f3-ce34-4d3b-8109-8093c9c7efb1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
