            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-4f1e054f-d3c9-4b14-aad6-e6efa5e575bd" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
