<p class="">Would the hon. Gentleman agree that the Scunthorpe steel mills <span id="1088" class="column-number" data-column-number="1088"></span> are among the most modern and best mills in the country? They were put up by men who really understood the trade and who had great foresight. Does he think those men will destroy what they have built?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
