<div class="content-item" id="contribution-f4c4424b-bc3f-4d6a-b5ed-4a5f8f655153">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-f4c4424b-bc3f-4d6a-b5ed-4a5f8f655153">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
